{"tid":2044215,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地傳銷搞手操控 港招打手","createTime":"2020-05-31T03:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T03:47:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"39172d3ec294ab1ab4f262a31a6044b8ada20928","tid":2044215,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200531/3C57YSWEREP3FJT2X3EG7AXJMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200531%2F3C57YSWEREP3FJT2X3EG7AXJMU%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdO4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=38c5efe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200531%2F3C57YSWEREP3FJT2X3EG7AXJMU%2F&h=d8930af4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200531/3C57YSWEREP3FJT2X3EG7AXJMU/</a><br />\n<br />\n內地傳銷搞手操控 港招打手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HWYBMN2E4H35RB7CJH6FW7IPFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHWYBMN2E4H35RB7CJH6FW7IPFM.jpg&h=960c14b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃鉦傑<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有資深加密貨幣炒家透露，在港吸金的加密貨幣，幕後主腦是一批活躍深圳的內地傳銷搞手，吸取早期香港傳銷香薰手法及倫敦金運作竅門，利用虛擬貨幣作新名堂斂財。「幣少」黃鉦傑亦是被招攬的打手，惟他涉高空撒錢事件被捕後聲名狼藉，改推朱公子上場，為獲投資者信任，更故意假扮幣少的死對頭。<br />\n<br />\n加密貨幣炒家阿倫稱，幣少及朱公子曾分別游說他合作推銷魔幣，惟阿倫認為魔幣不具投資價值及有斂財之嫌，故拒絕合作。後來魔。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n阿倫指本地幣圈約10萬人，活躍交易約3萬人。據他所知，兩年前彈起的幣少，曾從事傳銷及倫敦金，經幕後老細招攬後轉而推銷加密貨幣，在港設分區，再聘請6、7名年輕人充。。。。。。。。細遂推朱公子上場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加密貨幣欠監管易招損失<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：嘲受害人：儍婆，擺明做你<br />\n<br />\n據知，幣少曾吸引約百人投資，涉款1萬至80萬元。阿倫直指因監。。。。。。。。。。。。。股票起碼有證監（監管）」，騙徒利用這類數碼資產斂財，甚至造市。當交易涉欺詐，亦難追溯交易來源或核實有關人士身份，搜證及檢控困難，提醒「市場有好多光怪陸離嘅嘢，當未監管到，最好唔好沾手」。<br />\n<br />\n幣少去年3月涉售加密貨幣挖礦機騙案被捕，警方指該案件經調查後，以涉串謀詐騙拘捕三男，均拒保候查，三人暫獲釋，警方保留檢控權。<br />\n<br />\n加密貨幣<br />\n幣少爺<br />\n朱公子<br />\n魔幣"},{"pid":"c281e483ba3c9a3e1893e93b6246817605a20726","tid":2044215,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"其實比人呃既真係抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},{"pid":"b3f530e6364ca153ac603d99925379b98913f9ff","tid":2044215,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"幣少原來唔係自己有錢住豪宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1baf2dc58bc6ef15b52be2d336301526cbd8838","tid":2044215,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b3f530e6364ca153ac603d99925379b98913f9ff","tid":2044215,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"幣少原來唔係自己有錢住豪宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:38:37.000Z","msg":"你比幣笑呃左幾多？"},{"pid":"527ce928320e13f9196c14cf994edc4a633be769","tid":2044215,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:38:39.000Z","msg":"邊個係幣少幕後老細"},{"pid":"da97f94b9407975671638beff3b5a2771f48322f","tid":2044215,"uid":301100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"都唔知點解2020仲有傻莖會信d玩左幾十年嘅橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6715a55641f6f63c1dc1f3adc5719538889dc228","tid":2044215,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家YouTube 又成撚日彈個乜柒brian廣告出黎<br />\n<br />\n煩撚到嘔 咩我都賺夠啦 俾你賺下咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}